# Campaigns Folder (Legacy)

**Note:** This folder structure has been refactored. Campaigns now live under client folders.

**New structure:**
```
clients/
└── [client-name]/
    ├── brand-kit/              # Client-level brand files
    └── campaigns/              # All campaigns for this client
        └── [campaign-name]/
            └── output-assets/
```

See `clients/.gitkeep` for the new structure documentation.
